{"tid":1146671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比獨角獸還要夢幻的生物！！","createTime":"2019-05-09T11:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T13:06:49.000Z","uid":234662,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6196093a9b4b20583cb563bd0d04412e834495","tid":1146671,"uid":234662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:14:07.000Z","msg":"你寂寞嗎？有時候會覺得這世界上沒有任何人懂自己在想什麼，就連自己也不明白真正想要的是什麼，只能不斷書寫、在連登上低語著無人能理解的牢騷。這樣的你，並不孤單，世界上有一隻鯨魚也一樣地寂寞。<br />\n<br />\n他是52赫茲，世上最孤獨的鯨魚，即便生存在同一片海域裡，也沒有任何同類能聽見他的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就算沒有任何同類能聽見，也永遠不放棄說話的鯨魚</span></span><br />\n<br />\n鯨魚以聲納溝通，聲音頻率若是相通，就能進行對話。一般鯨魚的頻率大約在10－39赫茲之間，這頭最寂寞的鯨魚頻率卻高出一般鯨魚許多，是沒有人可以接收到的、只屬於自己的52赫茲。<br />\n公鯨魚們利用歌唱來求偶與社交，但「52赫茲」所吟詠的情歌從來沒有被誰聽懂，他的歌聲寂寞且潮濕，是心碎的自言自語，也是最寂寞的秘密。<br />\n就算與其他鯨魚同在一片海域中，卻始終沒有人能聽見他的52赫茲，他像是隱形一般地活著，只有毫不相關的人類知道它的存在，被人類發現20多年來，他的聲音令所有寂寞的人們想了都落淚。<br />\n傷心的事物永遠都是美麗的，這頭美麗且巨大的鯨魚在太平洋中默默潛行與移動，沒有伴侶與子女，他的生命寂靜無聲，卻仍不服輸般地拚命說話。<br />\n他持續的說話，讓我們知道他仍安好，讓我們知道他始終渴望著在這片海洋中，遇見一個能讀懂他的同伴。52赫茲，那是世界上最卑微也是最寂寞的歌聲，再往後的年歲中，他仍會繼續靜靜的發出其他鯨魚聽不到的聲音，一邊哭泣一邊盼望另一隻52赫茲的存在與呼應。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.storm.mg/amparticle/146572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Famparticle%2F146572&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=842114d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.storm.mg/amparticle/146572</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">活在大海裡也是萬幸，因為即使流淚，我也什麼都看不見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"00eafa9b0d5aba641bf27d87a58aa4993ad0fc51","tid":1146671,"uid":98387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:15:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ELS8Q_Ws3kU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DELS8Q_Ws3kU&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=621b7229\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ELS8Q_Ws3kU</a>"},{"pid":"33de71e904e8db5a6d840c6e76a27965d29fc4de","tid":1146671,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"試下第二個角度,既然都係要死,冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b9d20e9511b20dfe2591a9d536938431b0ec97","tid":1146671,"uid":234662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33de71e904e8db5a6d840c6e76a27965d29fc4de","tid":1146671,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"試下第二個角度,既然都係要死,冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:21:57.000Z","msg":"保持正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adf44a91a2caa5e8a559ee96f1d5b867be4f233","tid":1146671,"uid":234662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c338b033e62f6a924e4eebfe51afad551cb152a9","tid":1146671,"uid":234662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa975679f78cde3508466c735c6f59c8ad64f12f","tid":1146671,"uid":234662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3bc195402faa2dbcb7193d5fa3e2112658225627","tid":1146671,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0542KPyo1oY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0542KPyo1oY&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=93bf6706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0542KPyo1oY</a>"},{"pid":"f4b44ead10827b6a9622b0b4f39bd7b27400a4f7","tid":1146671,"uid":234662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:28:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68